<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1452,1938,2071]" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">
Herbs, perennial, procumbent. Stems subglabrous or strigose. Leaves opposite, sessile or shortly petiolate; blade 3- lobed, oblong, (2−) 
<quantity box="[357,444,1974,1999]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" unit="cm" value="6.5" valueMax="8.0" valueMin="5.0">5−8 cm</quantity>
long, (0.8−) 
<quantity box="[588,718,1974,1999]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" metricValueMax="2.5" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" unit="cm" value="2.0" valueMax="2.5" valueMin="1.5">1.5−2.5 cm</quantity>
broad, papery, sparsely strigose on both surfaces, base cuneate, apex acuminate, margin remotely serrulate. Capitula solitary on elongate peduncle, radiate; peduncle 
<quantity box="[1286,1386,2010,2035]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.05" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="0.6" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" unit="cm" value="10.5" valueMax="15.0" valueMin="6.0">6−15 cm</quantity>
long, strigose; involucre hemispheric, green; phyllaries 9−11, lanceolate, 2-seriate, subequal, 
<quantity box="[1119,1227,2046,2071]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.1" metricValueMin="0.9" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" unit="mm" value="10.0" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="9.0">9−11 mm</quantity>
long, strigose, apex
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[136,1451,160,221]" pageId="1" pageNumber="72">
acute. Ray florets 1-seriate, yellow; corolla 1.0− 
<quantity box="[682,758,160,185]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="1" pageNumber="72" unit="cm" value="1.2">1.2 cm</quantity>
long, 
<quantity box="[831,927,160,185]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="72" unit="mm" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3−4 mm</quantity>
broad, 2- or 3-dentate. Disk florets numerous, yellow; corolla 
<quantity box="[312,407,196,221]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="72" unit="mm" value="4.5" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="4.0">4−5 mm</quantity>
long, 5-lobed. Achenes unknown.
</paragraph>
